column5: Good morning folks! Hope you all have a great day!
Mornin' Roy, s'posed to rain all day here... but will still be a great day because we need the water!  ... to make those Spring flowers grow!!!
Good Morning  We are in a deep freeze this am.
You wouldn't be short of rain if you exercised a little foresight and stockpiled the rain like we do. I have about 11' of old rain all around the house here.
Have ya ever tried to melt snow in a cook pot to make water?
No Bubba...we have indoor plummin' here.
No wonder you thought you had 11 feet of rain then!

G'mornin' folks  That 11 feet of rain waiting to thaw reminds me of a Newfie joke...  Newf goes ice fishing and had a good catch. He brought home 100 pounds of ice and his wife drowned trying to cook it.  Have good day everyone.
Morning... I see that you and Lew both slept in today.
Yup, gettin lazy in my old age Corey, it was darned near 3:30 before I dragged myself outta bed this morning  Mornin boyz !!!!
have a great day yall. We are supposed to get some freezing rain down this way. Looking forward to the weekend!
Mornin all Cold this mornin but leavin work at noon to go walleye fishing and then goin after lakers on fri morning
Morning all,  I know its late but office work is a 9-5 job
Good Morning!  Hope everyone has a great day! Me too, tax time!
